		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">1.604</ph> Contracting Officer’s Representative (COR).</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p id="d62e13" class="- topic/p ">A contracting officer’s representative (COR) assists in the technical monitoring or administration of a contract (see <ph class="- topic/ph ">
					          <xref href="FAR-i1126427.dita#i1126427"
                     base="i1126427"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">1.602-2</xref>
				        </ph>(d)). The COR shall maintain a file for each assigned contract. The file must include, at a minimum–</p>
			      <ol id="d60e22" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d62e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A copy of the contracting officer’s letter of designation and other documents describing the COR’s duties and responsibilities;</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d62e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A copy of the contract administration functions delegated to a contract administration office which may not be delegated to the COR (see <xref href="FAR-i1126427.dita#i1126427"
                        base="i1126427"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">1.602-2</xref>(d)(4)); and</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d62e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Documentation of COR actions taken in accordance with the delegation of authority.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
